our company's standards.

352
00:26:43,500 --> 00:26:47,633
Emotion's not just a lingerie maker

353
00:26:47,700 --> 00:26:51,833
but a leader that maintains
the highest standard of beauty.

354
00:26:52,433 --> 00:26:56,533
