364
00:27:26,267 --> 00:27:28,300
Debauchery of the rich!

365
00:27:28,367 --> 00:27:30,800
You don't show off your underwear.

366
00:27:33,700 --> 00:27:36,333
-Why in the--
-What a big mouth.

367
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:45,133
