371
00:27:52,500 --> 00:27:54,167
"Why in the..."

372
00:27:58,100 --> 00:27:59,467
Why in the world

373
00:28:02,400 --> 00:28:03,767
do women have to

374
00:28:05,367 --> 00:28:08,167
