375
00:28:10,533 --> 00:28:12,033
Styling our hair,

376
00:28:12,967 --> 00:28:14,967
choosing cute clothes,

377
00:28:15,033 --> 00:28:17,100
taking time to put on makeup.

378
00:28:18,233 --> 00:28:20,633
Why wear expensive lingerie

379
00:28:20,700 --> 00:28:24,800
and make our breasts look bigger
and our body look sleek?

380
00:28:24,867 --> 00:28:28,133
