and look beautiful?

381
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:29,433
It's absurd!

382
00:28:29,500 --> 00:28:31,200
It's so unreasonable!

383
00:28:44,267 --> 00:28:45,633
Follow me.

384
00:29:02,467 --> 00:29:03,733
Look at this.

385
00:29:07,833 --> 00:29:09,500
Throughout human history,

386
00:29:09,567 --> 00:29:12,733
in Asia, Africa, North and South America,

387
00:29:12,800 --> 00:29:14,933
and of course Europe,

388
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,367
all women,

389
00:29:16,433 --> 00:29:19,100
in every age and every place,

390
00:29:19,167 --> 00:29:22,367
have been trying to be beautiful

391
00:29:22,433 --> 00:29:24,233
all through their existence.

392
00:29:25,533 --> 00:29:29,000
And humans have been admiring
the beauty of women.

393
00:29:30,233 --> 00:29:32,400
