394
00:29:35,500 --> 00:29:37,600
The human history

395
00:29:38,767 --> 00:29:39,933
is the answer.

396
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:33,633
Perfect place to mope.

397
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:39,600
I'm really sorry.

398
00:30:42,733 --> 00:30:47,767
