even though I don't know anything.

399
00:30:47,833 --> 00:30:49,667
No, you don't.

400
00:30:49,733 --> 00:30:52,167
You started just yesterday

401
00:30:52,233 --> 00:30:55,000
and negated the sensitive nature
of our job.

402
00:30:55,067 --> 00:30:56,733
We feel humiliated.

403
00:30:59,833 --> 00:31:01,867
My sincere apologies.

404
00:31:03,600 --> 00:31:05,800
Although, you do have a point.

405
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:13,567
No one knows for sure what beauty is.

406
00:31:14,500 --> 00:31:17,333
But, because no one knows,

407
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:20,667
someone like our boss, Mayumi Nanjo,

408
00:31:20,733 --> 00:31:23,700
has to keep pursuing it.

409
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:28,667
Otherwise, our world would be

410
00:31:28,767 --> 00:31:32,667
filled with ugly, cheap,
low quality stuff.

411
00:31:37,233 --> 00:31:39,233
Well, for now,

412
00:31:39,300 --> 00:31:41,367
