413
00:31:45,333 --> 00:31:46,400
Yes.

414
00:31:46,467 --> 00:31:48,667
The trunk show is coming.

415
00:31:48,733 --> 00:31:54,100
Our sales this season will be determined
by a dozen or so attendees there.

416
00:31:55,167 --> 00:31:57,567
So smile and do your best.

417
00:32:00,067 --> 00:32:01,300
Okay.

418
00:32:12,633 --> 00:32:14,200
No good.

419
00:32:21,633 --> 00:32:24,167
THREE DAYS TILL TRUNK SHOW

420
00:32:51,567 --> 00:32:54,267
-Good morning.
-Morning.

421
00:32:54,333 --> 00:32:56,400
