432
00:33:48,967 --> 00:33:52,733
Or use a less dense type
to make it lighter.

433
00:33:54,267 --> 00:33:55,700
No good.

434
00:33:56,300 --> 00:33:57,833
It's gym clothes.

435
00:33:57,900 --> 00:34:01,533
Gym clothes are evolving too.

436
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,667
You really are stubborn.

437
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:07,567
If you want beauty,

438
00:34:07,633 --> 00:34:12,867
printed rayon bare jersey
will have bright and beautiful colors.

439
00:34:12,933 --> 00:34:16,400
It has a different feel from silk
and drapes well.

440
00:34:16,467 --> 00:34:20,067
Stretchable, hygroscopic,
and beautiful.

441
00:34:20,133 --> 00:34:22,633
This is functional beauty.

442
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:27,000
"Functional beauty."

443
00:34:27,067 --> 00:34:28,233
Yes.

444
00:34:28,933 --> 00:34:30,100
Give it to me.

445
00:34:31,667 --> 00:34:32,667
Yes.

446
00:34:35,200 --> 00:34:36,767
I see.

447
00:34:36,833 --> 00:34:39,167
