Good night.

484
00:39:10,733 --> 00:39:13,400
<i>Why don't you say anything to her?</i>

485
00:39:13,467 --> 00:39:18,133
Well, because I can't compete with her.

486
00:39:18,233 --> 00:39:20,233
I doubt that.

487
00:39:20,300 --> 00:39:24,467
I think you have better taste.

488
00:39:25,300 --> 00:39:26,300
What?

489
00:39:31,567 --> 00:39:34,233
