495
00:39:50,100 --> 00:39:52,533
-Excuse me, this material--
-Ms. Sato.

496
00:39:52,633 --> 00:39:54,667
I'll use silk here.

497
00:39:55,700 --> 00:39:58,633
Is the color okay as it is?

498
00:39:58,700 --> 00:40:01,300
Wait, wait.
