510
00:40:33,867 --> 00:40:35,333
It's fun, isn't it?

511
00:41:00,567 --> 00:41:01,567
What are you doing?

512
00:41:05,133 --> 00:41:06,467
See you tomorrow.

513
00:41:08,300 --> 00:41:09,300
Excuse me.

514
00:41:15,700 --> 00:41:16,700
Well...

515
00:41:18,300 --> 00:41:21,267
