529
00:42:03,933 --> 00:42:06,100
It's fascinating because it's enigmatic.

530
00:42:07,267 --> 00:42:09,567
You're fascinating
because you're enigmatic.

531
00:42:10,433 --> 00:42:11,667
I'm flattered.

532
00:42:12,533 --> 00:42:15,400
Plus, I like this.

533
00:42:15,467 --> 00:42:19,167
